videos.description: PJ Washington gets open and knocks down a wide-open 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Washington is lethal from deep

videos.description: Riley Lachance finds Saben Lee on a backdoor cut and he throws down a vicious alley-oop.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt's Lee throws down monster jam

videos.description: Kevin Knox gets the steal and throws down a vicious two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Wildcats' Knox turns defense into offense

videos.description: Hamidou Diallo waits in the corner and Shai Gilgeous-Alexander finds him for the corner 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Diallo hits the dagger

videos.description: The No. 21 Wildcats have four starters score in double figures en route to a 74-67 victory.
videos.headline: Kentucky tops Vanderbilt on the road
